  "detailed_description": "In 2163, an asteroid hit Mars.<br>New gemstones were discovered there, and an unknown phenomenon occurred around the gemstones.<br>The V-Space company launched a project to send the mining robot Vidis to Mars to bring the gemstones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/f014ca3e4ece5b9b4cdfa27229ff0ca4.poster.avif?t=1730385751\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/f014ca3e4ece5b9b4cdfa27229ff0ca4.webm?t=1730385751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/f014ca3e4ece5b9b4cdfa27229ff0ca4.mp4?t=1730385751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join the Mission of Vidis, a robot miner who <strong>smashes rocks and mines Gemstones</strong>.<br>Classic <u>color-based puzzles</u> where simple rules, different strategies, and order are important.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/23e4bcbca93841d41f98ce10d15109ba.poster.avif?t=1730385751\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/23e4bcbca93841d41f98ce10d15109ba.webm?t=1730385751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/23e4bcbca93841d41f98ce10d15109ba.mp4?t=1730385751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>[1/5] Get a <strong>capsule</strong>, break down the <strong>same colored stones</strong> to make way and get <strong>Gemstones</strong> !<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/634aeb1419e61b32ac258da7ebf32552.poster.avif?t=1730385751\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/634aeb1419e61b32ac258da7ebf32552.webm?t=1730385751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/634aeb1419e61b32ac258da7ebf32552.mp4?t=1730385751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>[2/5] <strong>Create an expected route</strong> and explore the fastest route !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/a0dcb636648619f39642ee6965ae105f.poster.avif?t=1730385751\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/a0dcb636648619f39642ee6965ae105f.webm?t=1730385751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/a0dcb636648619f39642ee6965ae105f.mp4?t=1730385751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>[3/5] Plan your capsule acquisition sequence using <strong>Planner</strong> !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/0a4f258cd5019759f152c0f965da32f9.poster.avif?t=1730385751\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/0a4f258cd5019759f152c0f965da32f9.webm?t=1730385751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/0a4f258cd5019759f152c0f965da32f9.mp4?t=1730385751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>[4/5] Pick up the <strong>bomb</strong> and blast the stones blocking the road !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009240/extras/292fd67bfea62a0993b78c1803a0594a.avif?t=1730385751\" width=614 height=346 /></span><br><br>[5/5] Win <strong>106</strong> Gemstones ! <strong>Go back to the earth !</strong>",
